{"title":"Get Your Titanium Rainbow On with the Limited Edition WTC Morse Cage Ti","link":"https://bikerumor.com/titanium-rainbow-limited-edition-wtc-morse-cage-ti-bottle-cage/","date":1728410533000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WTC-Morse-Ti-CagesLimited-Rainbow-hero-jpeg.webp\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" alt=\"(Photo / Wolf Tooth Components)\" /></p>\n<p>The Minnesota Machining masterminds, Wolf Tooth Components (<a href=\"https://www.wolftoothcomponents.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WTC</a>), have released a <a href=\"https://www.wolftoothcomponents.com/products/morse-cage-ti-limited-edition-rainbow?utm_source=carousel&amp;utm_medium=homepage&amp;utm_campaign=position_1\" target=\"_blank\">limited run of rainbow-colored</a> titanium Morse Cages. They are in stock now and ready to go.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WTC-Morse-Ti-CagesLimited-Rainbow-redering-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WTC-Morse-Ti-CagesLimited-Rainbow-redering-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"WTC Morse Ti CagesLimited Rainbow redering\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WTC-Morse-Ti-CagesLimited-Rainbow-redering-jpeg.webp 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WTC-Morse-Ti-CagesLimited-Rainbow-redering-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WTC-Morse-Ti-CagesLimited-Rainbow-redering-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WTC-Morse-Ti-CagesLimited-Rainbow-redering-768x768.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photo / Wolf Tooth Components)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>The WTC Morse Cage</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The super versatile titanium <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/review-wolf-tooth-morse-cage-ti-bottle-cages/\" target=\"_blank\">Morse Cage</a> is made in the USA and uses a unique base plate that allows you to reposition the bottle placement on your bike. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WTC-Morse-Ti-CagesLimited-Rainbow-full-shot-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WTC-Morse-Ti-CagesLimited-Rainbow-full-shot-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"WTC Morse Ti CagesLimited Rainbow full shot\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WTC-Morse-Ti-CagesLimited-Rainbow-full-shot-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WTC-Morse-Ti-CagesLimited-Rainbow-full-shot-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WTC-Morse-Ti-CagesLimited-Rainbow-full-shot-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WTC-Morse-Ti-CagesLimited-Rainbow-full-shot-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WTC-Morse-Ti-CagesLimited-Rainbow-full-shot-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WTC-Morse-Ti-CagesLimited-Rainbow-full-shot-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This new, limited edition rainbow Morse Cage features a beautiful anodized rainbow finish. In case you didn’t know, the Morse cage gets its name from the base plate’s dot-dash-dot-dash mounting pattern. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WTC-Morse-Ti-CagesLimited-Rainbow-dot-dash-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WTC-Morse-Ti-CagesLimited-Rainbow-dot-dash-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"WTC Morse Ti CagesLimited Rainbow dot-dash\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WTC-Morse-Ti-CagesLimited-Rainbow-dot-dash-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WTC-Morse-Ti-CagesLimited-Rainbow-dot-dash-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WTC-Morse-Ti-CagesLimited-Rainbow-dot-dash-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WTC-Morse-Ti-CagesLimited-Rainbow-dot-dash-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WTC-Morse-Ti-CagesLimited-Rainbow-dot-dash-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WTC-Morse-Ti-CagesLimited-Rainbow-dot-dash-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The unique pattern on the plate offers four positions that align with your bike’s bottle bosses. Each of the four mounting options has a “dot” paired with a “dash” (like communicating with Morse Code). This gives you the option of up to 32mm of vertical adjustment of bottle cage positioning. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Limited Morse Cage Ti Retail and Features</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $90</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Limited Edition Rainbow anodized finish</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Hand-bent hollow titanium tubing</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Total weight of 33g (or roughly two CDs of your favorite speed metal)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Fits any frame that has a standard bottle cage mount with bolt spacing of 64mm (most modern frames)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Made here in our Minnesota machine shop</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Versatile option for bikes with multiple bottle cage mounts, full-suspension frames, smaller frames, and bikes with any size of frame bag</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Compatible with <a href=\"https://www.wolftoothcomponents.com/collections/b-rad-system/products/b-rad-bottle-relocation-and-accessory-device\" target=\"_blank\">Wolf Tooth B-RAD Mounting Bases</a> to adjust bottle positioning even further</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.wolftoothcomponents.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WolfToothComponents.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/titanium-rainbow-limited-edition-wtc-morse-cage-ti-bottle-cage/\">Get Your Titanium Rainbow On with the Limited Edition WTC Morse Cage Ti</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"d14a1c4e92e8abf0a2acefe7c27d5671ea977718ff927e7a32576ea1acd289b5","category":"Cycling"}